Steps To Reproduce:
1. Double clicking a node to open a corresponding diagram in another tab working in full GMF Editor

2. Used the same model to try and use this feature in RCP

3. Whwn double clicked on node got error: Cannot open input element: Reason: Error a blank empty tab opened


More information:
Used build as of: http://download.eclipse.org/modeling/gmf/downloads/drops/N-N20070115-200701150603/index.php

summary of model used

A: Diagram/Canvas, contains B and C nodes, attribute: Name

B: Node, can link to B nodes, can link to C nodes, attribute: Name

C: Node, extends A, can link to B nodes, Canvas Mapping
(in full editor when double clicked opens another canvas A)
